dct_title_s: Cabanatuan, Philippine Islands, Nueva Ecija Province, Luzon. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 1. Alternate title: Cabanatuan. Polyconic projection, projection ticks approximate. In upper left margin: Philippine city plans 1:5,00 (approx.). Compiled from Map of Cabanatuan, Manila Fire Insurance Association; Luzon, 1:31,680, Office Dept. Eng. Phil. Dept., no. 28C, 1910; vertical photograph, 1940; oblique photographs, 1940.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
